pearance-3317744" target="_blank" rel="noopener">出现在伊比沙岛的一家夜总会</a>翻唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/britney-spears" target="_blank" rel="noopener">布兰妮·斯皮尔斯</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/backstreet-boys" target="_blank" rel="noopener">后街男孩</a>的歌曲。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-gatecrash-las-vegas-wedding-perform-magical-3496249">观看艾德·希兰在拉斯维加斯婚礼上表演“Magical”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
